<h4>
<a name="docs-ingles"></a>
Documentos em Inglês
</h4>

<h5>
Documentos do CERT/CC
</h5>

<ul>

  <li> <a href="http://www.cert.org/csirts/">
       CERT/CC CSIRT Development Team</a><br /> </li>

  <li> <a href="http://www.cert.org/csirts/services.html"> CSIRT
       Services</a><br /> </li>

  <li> <a href="http://www.cert.org/archive/pdf/07tr008.pdf">Incident
       Management Capability Metrics Version 0.1</a> [PDF]
       <br /> </li>

  <li> <a href="http://www.cert.org/archive/pdf/08tr007.pdf">
       Incident Management Mission Diagnostic Method</a> [PDF]
       <br /> </li>

  <li> <a href="http://www.cert.org/csirts/action_list.html">Action
       List for Developing a Computer Security Incident Response Team
       (CSIRT)</a>
       <br /> </li>

  <li> <a
       href="http://www.cert.org/archive/pdf/NationalCSIRTs.pdf">Steps
       for Creating National CSIRTs</a> [PDF]
       <br /> </li>

  <li> <a
       href="http://www.sei.cmu.edu/publications/documents/03.reports/03hb002.html">
       Handbook for Computer Security Incident Response Teams (CSIRTs)
       -- 2nd Edition</a><br /> </li>

  <li> <a href="http://www.cert.org/archive/pdf/04tr015.pdf">Defining
       Incident Management Processes for CSIRTs: A Work in
       Progress</a>
       <br /> </li>

  <li> Organizational Models for Computer Security Incident Response
       Teams <a
       href="http://www.cert.org/archive/pdf/03hb001.pdf">[PDF]</a>
       <a
       href="http://www.sei.cmu.edu/publications/documents/03.reports/03hb001.html">[HTML]</a>
       <br /> </li>

  <li> <a href="http://www.cert.org/csirts/csirt-staffing.html">
       Staffing Your Computer Security Incident Response Team? What
       Basic Skills Are Needed?</a>
       <br /> </li>

  <li> State of the Practice of Computer Security Incident
       Response Teams (CSIRTs)
       <a href="http://www.cert.org/archive/pdf/03tr001.pdf">[PDF]</a>
       <a
href="http://www.sei.cmu.edu/publications/documents/03.reports/03tr001.html">[HTML]</a>
       <br /> </li>

  <li> <a href="http://www.cert.org/csirts/resources.html">Coletânea
       de artigos, projetos e instituições relacionadas com CSIRTs</a>
       <br /> </li>

</ul>

<h5>
Documentos de outras fontes
</h5>


<ul>

  <li> <a
       href="http://csrc.nist.gov/publications/nistpubs/800-61/sp800-61.pdf">
       Computer Security Incident Handling Guide</a>, NIST
       <br /> </li>

  <li> <a
       href="http://www.auscert.org.au/render.html?it=2252&amp;cid=1938">
       Forming an Incident Response Team</a>, AusCERT
       <br /> </li>

  <li> <a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2196.txt">
       RFC 2196: Site Security Handbook</a>
       <br /> </li>

  <li> <a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2350.txt">
       RFC 2350: Expectations for Computer Security Incident
       Response</a>
       </li>

</ul>

